WEBVTT

00:03.202 --> 00:04.703
If anyone should
be getting married,

00:04.737 --> 00:07.306
it should be Ricky and me,
not Adrian and Ben.

00:07.340 --> 00:09.308
This is my mother.
This is Nora.

00:09.342 --> 00:11.510
Nora, George.
George, Nora.

00:11.544 --> 00:13.178
How's six weeks from today?

00:13.212 --> 00:14.479
For?

00:14.514 --> 00:16.381
Ben, for the wedding.

00:16.416 --> 00:18.717
I think you're a really
interesting woman.

00:18.751 --> 00:20.719
I don't think
I've ever met anyone
who's been to prison.

00:20.753 --> 00:23.288
Oh, you probably have.
Maybe.

00:23.323 --> 00:25.691
I asked Adrian to marry me,
and she said yes,

00:25.725 --> 00:28.960
and we're getting married,
and when and where
are her decisions.

00:28.995 --> 00:32.197
Adrian wants our son
to be ringbearer at this circus,

00:32.231 --> 00:34.066
and she wants Amy
to be a bridesmaid.

00:34.100 --> 00:36.234
My dad's okay
with your coming over

00:36.269 --> 00:38.570
as long as we're not doing
what we were doing.

00:38.604 --> 00:41.707
Would it be stupid
if the two of us
actually had sex?

00:41.741 --> 00:43.709
I thought you wanted me
to sleep over
so we could have sex.

00:43.743 --> 00:45.243
I don't wanna have sex
with any guy

00:45.278 --> 00:46.912
unless there's a chance
we're gonna get married.

00:46.946 --> 00:48.413
I think it would be better

00:48.448 --> 00:50.549
if we asked my dad

00:50.583 --> 00:52.551
to buy us a condo.

00:52.585 --> 00:53.985
A condo?

00:54.020 --> 00:55.387
Ricky,

00:57.056 --> 00:58.724
will you marry me?

